labels.name: P2: Fix can wait a while

data.actual_result: Discord will come up with it's crash menu, continuing will restart Discord.
data.expected_result: Shows you that the AFK channel was set to nothing.
data.short_description: Opening the audit log entry for changing the AFK channel to nothing will crash Discord.
data.steps_to_repro: - Set the AFK channel to 'No AFK Channel' - Enter your audit log, and click the drop-down for the server change.
